title: ArtyTorrent Pack 64-Ueberschall House Essentials FX 2-WAV sample
description:
ArtyTorrent Pack 64-Ueberschall House Essentials FX 2-WAV samples
-----------------------------------------------------------------

This completes the upload of the full Ueberschall House Essentials sample disc. This is a bonus pack of uncategorized sound effect oneshots that could be used in many genres of music, not just house. Have fun sorting the zaps from the whooshes!

Torrent contains 1 RAR file with 444 FX samples
-----------------------------------------------
Ueb HE More FX.RAR (143MB)

All samples are normalized 16-bit WAVs at 44.1KHz.

--
Arty - "Sweep the house!"
15th February 2008.
